{"type": "article", "id": 14108, "title": "自行车智能导航器", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-28T07:27:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125739RmoMg4hSzHKCI3rd.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tSmarthalo 是 Cyclelabs 推出的一款可以把普通自行车变成智能自行车的导航器，它采用的是一个 LED 导航系统，通过灯的颜色变幻，带领你到达目的地，比如右侧绿光半圆表示准备右转，闪烁表示现在右转，下方亮起红光半圆表示U型转等等。其次，与智能手机连接后，可以记录里程，路线等信息，同时具备防水防盗的性能。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1106460188/smarthalo-turn-your-bike-into-a-smart-bike%E2%80%8B\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141712aASWN0sR9PQuO1CH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141713VJOhxprXBf2FIad9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141714Citky2BRIdNFXUcG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141714qYaBogbD12hOpmxC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141715xawR3WTXDNCl4jAK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141715nQm0eabBEVj7lpdP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141716u463kbW7DxocGI0l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61369193\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}